<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_ee377ff2e0cc.aspx"><b>狱中赠邹容</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e6%b8%85%e4%bb%a3">清代</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e7%ab%a0%e7%82%b3%e9%ba%9f">章炳麟</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonee377ff2e0cc">
邹容吾小弟，被发下瀛州。<br />快剪刀除辫，干牛肉作餱。<br />英雄一入狱，天地亦悲秋。<br />临命须掺手，乾坤只两头！
</div>
