<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_c55b372b8545.aspx"><b>初晴游沧浪亭</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%ae%8b%e4%bb%a3">宋代</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e8%8b%8f%e8%88%9c%e9%92%a6">苏舜钦</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonc55b372b8545">
夜雨连明春水生，娇云浓暖弄阴晴。<br />帘虚日薄花竹静，时有乳鸠相对鸣。
